Subject: RE: [VB] ARC vs. MIG - torsion bars

According to the 63-67 Bentleys, the welded end torsion bars are the
replacement for the separate leaf bars. Separate leaf bars were to be used
until stocks ran out, but the welded end bars were preferred.

